Comment: 1,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.88,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,I was daydreaming by the window
Comment: 1,0:21:29.88,0:21:34.48,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,She and I, alone in the classroom
Comment: 1,0:21:34.48,0:21:37.20,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,Staring from opposite corners of the room
Comment: 1,0:21:37.20,0:21:41.44,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,At her peaceful eyes and her fragrant hair
Comment: 1,0:21:41.68,0:21:44.64,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,It’s three o’clock, and I’m sweating a lot
Comment: 1,0:21:44.64,0:21:49.31,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,Is our storm brewing, or is it just hot?
Comment: 1,0:21:49.31,0:21:52.00,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,I feel like I’m close enough to touch you
Comment: 1,0:21:52.00,0:21:55.76,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,But even one meter is a meter too far
Comment: 1,0:21:56.22,0:22:00.16,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,Is she cool? Kind? One to share secrets with?
Comment: 1,0:22:00.16,0:22:03.74,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,It’s not good to make assumptions based on one’s image
Comment: 1,0:22:03.74,0:22:08.11,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,So rather than mulling over whether to make them a friend
Comment: 1,0:22:08.11,0:22:12.36,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,Just talk to them
Comment: 1,0:22:12.36,0:22:16.52,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,Ah, being wrong is just fine, just fine
Comment: 1,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.73,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,You have to have true sympathy for each other
Comment: 1,0:22:19.73,0:22:23.86,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,I’m starting to get that feeling, that feeling
Comment: 1,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.15,EDENG,,0,0,0,karaoke,That something’s bound to happen
